Hydrology data from GEODATA TOPO 250K Series 3

Source: R/data.R
qld_hydro.Rd

This is a subset of the original GEODATA TOPO 250K Series 3 dataset made available by Geoscience Australia. The original GEODATA TOPO 250K Series 3 is a vector representation of the major topographic features appearing on the 1:250,000 scale NATMAPs supplied in Shape file format and is designed for use in a range of commercial GIS software. Data is arranged within specific themes. All data is based on the GDA2020 coordinate system.

Format

A Simple Features data.frame with 496,036 rows and 17 variables:

  • OBJECTID:

  • FEATTYPE:

  • TYPE:

  • NAME:

  • PERENNIAL:

  • HIERARCHY:

  • FEATREL:

  • ATTRREL:

  • PLANACC:

  • SOURCE:

  • CREATED:

  • RETIRED:

  • PID:

  • SYMBOL:

  • TEXTNOTE:

  • SHAPE_Leng:

  • geometry:
